Package com.platform.auth.internal

Class OAuth2AuditEvent

java.lang.Object
com.platform.auth.internal.OAuth2AuditEvent
@Entity public class OAuth2AuditEvent extends Object
OAuth2 Audit Event entity for compliance logging and security monitoring Records all OAuth2-related activities for audit trails and forensic analysis

This entity supports GDPR compliance by tracking user consent and data processing activities while providing comprehensive audit trails for security monitoring.
